9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"No Game, No Life | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"Bored with life and considering the real world to be just a “crappy game,” savvy sibling shut-ins Sora and Shiro have withdrawn into their own fantasy world filled with video games. \n<br><br>\nHowever, one day they find themselves summoned to another world by a boy who calls himself “God,” their abilities are about to be put to the ultimate test! Now not only their fates — but the fate of all of humanity — will be decided by a series of games that may just be the hardest these super-geniuses have ever faced!\n<br><br>\n(Source: Sentai Filmworks, edited)"}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/series/149112/no-game-no-life"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"No Game, No Life"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"Bored with life and considering the real world to be just a “crappy game,” savvy sibling shut-ins Sora and Shiro have withdrawn into their own fantasy world filled with video games. \n<br><br>\nHowever, one day they find themselves summoned to another world by a boy who calls himself “God,” their abilities are about to be put to the ultimate test! Now not only their fates — but the fate of all of humanity — will be decided by a series of games that may just be the hardest these super-geniuses have ever faced!\n<br><br>\n(Source: Sentai Filmworks, edited)"}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/series/149112/no-game-no-life"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b19815-sEOQ9yQaPKlk.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","cont